{"tid":2098634,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男拔小學部有家長確診　中小學明起停課","createTime":"2020-07-07T15:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T15:44:19.000Z","uid":212626,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0efbb6d5a7efba9b369966f282968dae4002bfbd","tid":2098634,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:22:54.000Z","msg":"拔萃男書院校長鄭基恩在學校網頁公布，小學部一名家長確診新型肺炎，考慮到學生安全，該校小學部及中學部明天起停課，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n校方表示，原定明日舉行的考試亦會取消，稍後再通知考試安排，校園將進行全面清潔和消毒，建議學生留在家中讀書。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536400-20200707.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536400-20200707.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=123c060c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536400-20200707.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c3bdc04d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536400-20200707.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ffec2c857e4583804a166f05eb366e1078459649","tid":2098634,"uid":1249,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:26:18.000Z","msg":"全港停算啦屌"},{"pid":"0d3f3139fc76889421f3b024dc98623cf5e944a8","tid":2098634,"uid":236368,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"你地班離地同深藍深紅仲唔收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7c813ceb556e0786be23019b40b2a8792f7fc8","tid":2098634,"uid":293529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:27:33.000Z","msg":"以為全港"},{"pid":"0d25a0d36dd00a78d25ea511a28358031057ec9a","tid":2098634,"uid":136900,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:27:56.000Z","msg":"直接停撚佢算啦屌 都7月啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18cb2c86c70dd7821212d7565709fecde0b1ffdf","tid":2098634,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f7c813ceb556e0786be23019b40b2a8792f7fc8","tid":2098634,"uid":293529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:27:33.000Z","msg":"以為全港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:28:46.000Z","msg":"男拔中小學部"},{"pid":"9854392f5f4999f4c905729d6b35fca8311a34cd","tid":2098634,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:29:21.000Z","msg":"我要去海洋公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3256bbf152840e3fcc4b3b5320018e891b987306","tid":2098634,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:33:18.000Z","msg":"拔萃男書院中小學部星期三起停課<br />\n<br />\n拔萃男書院宣布，由於小學部有一名家長確診感染新型冠狀病毒，考慮到學生安全，決定小學部及中學部明天起停課，直至另行通知。校方表示，原定星期三舉行的考試亦會取消，稍後再通知考試安排，校舍將進行全面清潔和消毒，建議學生留在家中溫習。<br />\n<br />\n另外，位於海泓道的油蔴地天主教小學宣布，一個與校內兩名分別小一和小五學生同住的親友，對病毒初步呈陽性反應，正等候覆檢，為安全起見，學校明日停課一天，以作徹底消毒及清潔。保良局林文燦英文小學亦宣布，一名六年級學生的媽媽今晚初步確診，學校星期三停課一天。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2345888&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=53a0bb92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345888</a>"},{"pid":"00b2183827d89d6275db02149a168c3771856b91","tid":2098634,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3256bbf152840e3fcc4b3b5320018e891b987306","tid":2098634,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:33:18.000Z","msg":"拔萃男書院中小學部星期三起停課<br />\n<br />\n拔萃男書院宣布，由於小學部有一名家長確診感染新型冠狀病毒，考慮到學生安全，決定小學部及中學部明天起停課，直至另行通知。校方表示，原定星期三舉行的考試亦會取消，稍後再通知考試安排，校舍將進行全面清潔和消毒，建議學生留在家中溫習。<br />\n<br />\n另外，位於海泓道的油蔴地天主教小學宣布，一個與校內兩名分別小一和小五學生同住的親友，對病毒初步呈陽性反應，正等候覆檢，為安全起見，學校明日停課一天，以作徹底消毒及清潔。保良局林文燦英文小學亦宣布，一名六年級學生的媽媽今晚初步確診，學校星期三停課一天。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2345888&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=53a0bb92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345888</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"又多間保良局林文燦英文小學<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d459c1551b24dd44c36927afe1ef2571a5e5537","tid":2098634,"uid":152705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"樓股又gogogo 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb3633b1223333c8af6ee58c63a783458a9e9f1","tid":2098634,"uid":166474,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:38:00.000Z","msg":"痴撚線, 家長確診都要中小學一齊停, 比美國聽到實笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17288cd1b9eb00557ee1d996b25975a2122b778c","tid":2098634,"uid":29929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7fb3633b1223333c8af6ee58c63a783458a9e9f1","tid":2098634,"uid":166474,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:38:00.000Z","msg":"痴撚線, 家長確診都要中小學一齊停, 比美國聽到實笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:44:19.000Z","msg":"本身呢間學校學生<br />\n返同唔返對學業成績唔大影響架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}